violation_severity.cellBackground:
{{data_table.processedTableData.map((currentRow, currentIndex) => ( 
  currentRow["violation_severity"] === "Very Low" ? "#FFF9C4" : 
  currentRow["violation_severity"] === "Low" ? "#FFECB3" : 
  currentRow["violation_severity"] === "Medium" ? "#FFE082" : 
  currentRow["violation_severity"] === "High" ? "#FFD54F" : 
  currentRow["violation_severity"] === "Very High" ? "#FFCDD2" : 
  "#FFFFFF" // default color if none of the conditions are met
))}}
violation_severity.label: Severity
